OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will move
OL,6,Feastwards throughout Wednesday,
OL,7,Fbecoming slow-moving across parts of
OL,8,FScotland. A mix of sunshine and
OL,9,Fshowers following, most frequent
OL,10,Fshowers likely in the north with hail
OL,11,Fand thunder possible for many. Windy
OL,12,Ffor most areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FFurther showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain likely into the evening
OL,16,Fand overnight, some clear spells
OL,17,Flikely across the east of the Country.
OL,18,FRemaining rather breezy and mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
