OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRemaining breezy on Thursday
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers, however
OL,7,Fthese merging at times to give longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain, and possibly the odd
OL,9,Frumble of thunder. Near normal
OL,10,Ftemperatures.
